      "content": "I was being overly cautious, and I appreciate you bringing this to my attention. The actual time required for the patch and reboot is indeed 5-6 hours, and I should have been more accurate in my initial assessment. However, I've spoken with the lead engineer, and we're confident that we can expedite the process by working around the clock and utilizing our on-call support team to minimize the downtime. We'll also be using a temporary workaround to ensure business continuity, which will allow us to keep the service online for a short period while we complete the patch. This way, we can still meet our SLA commitments and minimize the impact on our customers.",
